title: Infected Tomb of the Storm Messiah
story: The tomb of the Storm Messiah is situated high in the Eskara mountain peaks. Now it is controlled by a band of thugs. It is rumored that countless treasures of magical artifacts and gold are stored here.

notes.text: A great stone door with two keyholes to the west.
A skinless body of a halfling, a key close by.
A key tucked under some debris.
